quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  42,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  42,1,Haa-Meeem
  42,2,Ayyn seen Qaaf
  42,3,khuday-e ghalib o Dana isi terhan tumhari taraf mazameen aur ( Buraheen ) bhejta hai jis terhan tum se pehlay logon ki taraf wahi bhejta raha hai
  42,4,jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab isi ka hai. aur woh aliiiii rutba aur graami qader hai
  42,5,qareeb hai ke aasman oopar se phatt parrin aur farishtay apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath is kitasbih karte rehtay hain aur jo log zameen mein hain un ke liye maffi mangte rehtay hain. sun rakho ke khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  42,6,aur jin logon ne is ke siwa karsaaz bana rakhay hain woh khuda ko yaad hain. aur tum un par Darogha nahi ho
  42,7,aur isi terhan tumahray paas quran arabi bheja hai taakay tum barray gaon ( yani mukkay ) ke rehne walon ko aur jo log is ke ird gird rehtay hain un ko rasta dikhao aur inhen qayamat ke din ka bhi jis mein kuch shak nahi hai khauf dlao. is roz aik fareeq bahisht mein hoga aur aik fareeq dozakh mein
  42,8,aur agar khuda chahta to un ko aik hi jamaat kardaita lekin woh jis ko chahta hai apni rehmat mein daakhil karleta hai aur zaalmon ka nah koi yaar hai aur nah madadgaar
  42,9,kiya unhon ne is ke siwa karsaaz banaye hain? karsaaz to khuda hi hai aur wohi mardon ko zindah kere ga aur woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  42,10,aur tum jis baat mein ikhtilaaf karte ho is ka faisla khuda ki taraf ( se hoga ) yahi khuda mera perwar-digaar hai mein isi par bharosa rakhta hon. aur isi ki taraf rujoo karta hon
  42,11,asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala ( wohi hai ). isi ne tumahray liye tumhari hi jins ke jore banaye aur charpayon ke bhi jore ( banaye aur ) isi tareeq par tum ko phelata rehta hai. is jaisi koi cheez nahi. aur woh daikhta santa hai
  42,12,asmano aur zameen ki knjyan isi ke haath mein hain. woh jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq farakh kardaita hai ( aur jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai. be shak woh har cheez se waaqif hai
  42,13,isi ne tumahray liye deen ka wohi rasta muqarrarkiya jis ( ke ikhtiyar karne ka ) Nooh ko hukum diya tha aur jis ki ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tumhari taraf wahi bhaije hai aur jis ka ibrahim aur moose aur eesa ko hukum diya tha ( woh yeh ) ke deen ko qaim rakhna aur is mein phoot nah daalna. jis cheez ki taraf tum mushrikon ko bulatay ho woh un ko dushwaar guzarti hai. allah jis ko chahta hai apni bargaah ka bargzida karleta hai aur jo is ki taraf rujoo kere usay apni taraf rasta dikha deta hai
  42,14,aur yeh log jo allag allag hue hain to ilm ( haq ) aa Chuknay ke baad aapas ki zid se ( hue hain ). aur agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye baat nah thehr chuki hoti to un mein faisla kardiya jata. aur jo log un ke baad ( khuda ki ) kitaab ke waris hue woh is ( ki taraf ) se shubhay ki uljan mein ( phansay hue ) hain
  42,15,to ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) isi ( deen ki ) taraf ( logon ko ) bulatay rehna aur jaissa tum ko hukum howa hai ( isi par ) qaim rehna. aur un ki khawahishon ki pairwi nah karna. aur keh do ke jo kitaab khuda ne nazil farmai hai mein is par imaan rakhta hon. aur mujhe hukum howa hai ke tum mein insaaf karoon. khuda hi hamara aur tumhara perwar-digaar hai. hum ko hamaray aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumahray aamaal ka. hum mein aur tum mein kuch behas o takraar nahi. khuda hum ( sab ) ko akatha kere ga. aur isi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  42,16,aur jo log khuda ( ke baray ) mein baad is ke ke usay ( mominoun ne ) maan liya ho jhagarte hain un ke perwar-digaar ke nazdeek un ka jhagra laghu hai. aur un par ( khuda ka ) ghazab aur un ke liye sakht azaab hai
  42,17,khuda hi to hai jis ne sachaai ke sath kitaab nazil farmai aur ( Adal vansaf ki ) traazo. aur tum kokiya maloom shayad qayamat qareeb hi aa pohanchi ho
  42,18,jo log is par imaan nahi rakhtay woh is ke liye jaldi kar rahay hain. aur jo momin hain woh is se drtay hain. aur jantay hain ke woh brhq hai. dekho jo log qayamat mein jhagarte hain woh parlay darjay ki gumraahi mein hain
  42,19,khuda apne bundon par meharban hai woh jis ko chahta hai rizaq deta hai. aur woh zor wala ( aur ) zabardast hai
  42,20,jo shakhs akhirat ki khaiti ka khawastgah ho is ko hum is mein se den ge. aur jo duniya ki khaiti ka khawastgah ho is ko hum is mein se day den ge. aur is ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nah hoga
  42,21,kiya un ke woh shareek hain jinhon ne un ke liye aisa deen muqarrarkiya hai jis ka khuda ne hukum nahi diya. aur agar faislay ( ke din ) ka wada nah hota to un mein faisla kardiya jata aur jo zalim hain un ke liye dard dainay wala azaab hai
  42,22,tum dekho ge ke zalim apne aamaal ( ke wabaal ) se dar rahay hon ge aur woh un par parre ga. aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay woh bahisht ke baghoon mein hon ge. woh jo kuch chahain ge un ke liye un ke perwar-digaar ke paas ( mojood ) hoga. yahi bara fazl hai
  42,23,yahi woh ( inaam hai ) jis ki khuda apne un bundon ko jo imaan laatay aur amal naik karte hain basharat deta hai. keh do ke mein is ka tum se sila nahi mangta magar ( tum ko ) qaraabat ki mohabbat ( to chahiye ) aur jo koi neki kere ga hum is ke liye is mein sawab barhayain ge. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala qadar daan hai
  42,24,kiya yeh log kehte hain ke paighambar ne khuda par jhoot bandh liya hai? agar khuda chahay to ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tumahray dil par mohar laga day. aur khuda jhoot ko nabood karta aur apni baton se haq ko saabit karta hai. be shak woh seenay taq ki baton se waaqif hai
  42,25,aur wohi to hai jo apne bundon ki tauba qubool karta aur ( un ke ) qasoor maaf farmata hai aur jo tum karte ho ( sab ) jaanta hai
  42,26,aur jo imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye un ki ( dua ) qubool farmata hai aur un ko apne fazl se berhata hai. aur jo kafir hain un ke liye sakht azaab hai
  42,27,aur agar khuda apne bundon ke liye rizaq mein farakhi kardaita to zameen mein fasaad karne lagtay. lekin woh jo cheez chahta hai andazay ke sath nazil karta hai. be shak woh apne bundon ko jaanta aur daikhta hai
  42,28,aur wohi to hai jo logon ke na umeed hojane ke baad meen brsata aur apni rehmat ( yani barish ) ki barket ko phela deta hai. aur woh karsaaz aur sazawar tareef hai
  42,29,aur isi ki nshanyon mein se hai asmano aur zameen ka peda karna aur un janwaron ka jo is ne un mein phela rakhay hain aur woh jab chahay un ke jama kar lanay par Qadir hai
  42,30,aur jo museebat tum par waqay hoti hai so tumahray apne faylon se aur woh bohat se gunah to maaf hi kardaita hai
  42,31,aur tum zameen mein ( khuda ko ) aajiz nahi kar saktay. aur khuda ke siwa nah tumhara koi dost hai aur nah madadgaar
  42,32,aur isi ki nshanyon mein se samandar ke jahaaz hain ( jo ) goya pahar ( hain )
  42,33,agar khuda chahay to howa ko tehraa dey aur jahaaz is ki satah par kharray reh jayen. tamam sabr aur shukar karne walon ke liye un ( baton ) mein qudrat khuda ke namoonay hain
  42,34,ya un ke aamaal ke sabab un ko tabah kardey. aur bohat se qasoor maaf kardey
  42,35,aur ( intiqam is liye liya jaye ke ) jo log hamari aayton mein jhagarte hain. woh jaan len ke un ke liye khulasi nahi
  42,36,( logo ) jo ( maal o mata'a) tum ko diya gaya hai woh duniya ki zindagi ka ( napaidaar ) faida hai. aur jo kuch khuda ke haan hai woh behtar aur qaim rehne wala hai ( yani ) un logon ke liye jo imaan laaye aur apne perwar-digaar par bhrosa rakhtay hain
  42,37,aur jo barray barray gunaaho aur be hiyai ki baton se parhaiz karte hain. aur jab gussa aata hai to maaf kardete hain
  42,38,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ka farmaan qubool karte hain aur namaz parhte hain. aur apne kaam aapas ke mashwaray se karte hain. aur jo maal hum ne un ko ataa farmaya hai is mein se kharch karte hain
  42,39,aur jo aisay hain ke jab un par zulm وتعدی ho to ( munhasib tareeqay se ) badla letay hain
  42,40,aur buraiee ka badla to isi terhan ki buraiee hai. magar jo dar guzar kere aur ( muamlay ko ) durust kardey to is ka badla khuda ke zimmay hai. is mein shak nahi ke woh zulm karne walon ko pasand nahi karta
  42,41,aur jis par zulm howa ho agar woh is ke baad intiqam le to aisay logon par kuch ilzaam nahi
  42,42,ilzaam to un logon par hai jo logon par zulm karte hain aur malik mein na-haq fasaad pheilatay hain. yahi log hain jin ko takleef dainay wala azaab hoga
  42,43,aur jo sabr kere aur qasoor maaf kardey to yeh himmat ke kaam hain
  42,44,aur jis shakhs ko khuda gumraah kere to is ke baad is ka koi dost nahi. aur tum zaalmon ko dekho ge ke jab woh ( dozakh ka ) azaab dekhen ge to kahin gekiya ( duniya mein ) wapas jaane ki bhi koi Sabeel hai ?
  42,45,aur tum un ko dekho ge ke dozakh ke samnay laaye jayen ge zillat se aajzi karte hue chhupi ( aur neechi ) nigah se dekh rahay hon ge. aur momin log kahin ke ke khasara uthany walay to woh hain jinhon ne qayamat ke din apne aap ko aur apne ghar walon ko khasaray mein dala. dekho ke be insaaf log hamesha ke dukh mein ( parre ) rahen ge
  42,46,aur khuda ke siwa un ke koi dost nah hon ge ke khuda ke siwa un ko madad day saken. aur jis ko khuda gumraah kere is ke liye ( hadaayat ka ) koi rasta nahi
  42,47,un se keh do ke ) qabal is ke ke woh din jo talle ga nahi khuda ki taraf se aa mojood ho apne perwar-digaar ka hukum qubool karo. is din tumahray liye nah koi jaye panah hogi aur nah tum se gunaaho ka inkaar hi ban parre ga
  42,48,phir agar yeh munh phair len to hum ne tum ko un par nigehbaan bana kar nahi bheja. tumhara kaam to sirf ( ehkaam ka ) pouncha dena hai. aur jab hum ensaan ko apni rehmat ka maza chukhate hain to is se khush hojata hai. aur agar un ko un hi ke aamaal ke sabab koi sakhti pahunchti hai to ( sab ehsaanon ko bhool jatay hain ) be shak ensaan bara nashukara hai
  42,49,( tamam ) badshahat khuda hi ki hai asmano ki bhi aur zameen ki bhi. woh jo chahta hai peda karta hai. jisay chahta hai betiyan ataa karta hai aur jisay chahta hai betay bkhshta hai
  42,50,ya un ko betay aur betiyan dono inayat farmata hai. aur jis ko chahta hai be aulaad rakhta hai. woh to jan-nay wala ( aur ) qudrat wala hai
  42,51,aur kisi aadmi ke liye mumkin nahi ke khuda is se baat kere magar ilham ( ke zariye ) se ya parday ke peechay se ya koi farishta bhaij day to woh khuda ke hukum se jo khuda chahay alqa kere. be shak woh aliiiii rutba ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  42,52,aur isi terhan hum ne apne hukum se tumhari taraf rooh al quds ke zariye se ( quran ) bheja hai. tum nah to kitaab ko jantay they aur nah imaan ko. lekin hum ne is ko noor banaya hai ke is se hum apne bundon mein se jis ko chahtay hain hadaayat karte hain. aur be shak ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum seedha rasta dikhata ho
  42,53,( yani ) khuda ka rasta jo asmano aur zameen ki sab cheezon ka maalik hai. dekho sab kaam khuda ki taraf rujoo hon ge ( aur wohi un mein faisla kere ga )
